he</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1447684664/image_1447684664.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742345-gaotu-techedu-profitability-has-reached-bottom-maintain-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 18:21:38"}, {"id": "4742344", "title": "Stride: Is Valuation Now A Risk?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1731919436/image_1731919436.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Ladder of success concept\" data-id=\"1731919436\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1731919436/image_1731919436.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1731919436/image_1731919436.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1731919436/image_1731919436.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1731919436/image_1731919436.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1731919436/image_1731919436.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1731919436/image_1731919436.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1731919436/image_1731919436.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1731919436/image_1731919436.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>Nearly three months have passed since I wrote my first article in Seeking Alpha about <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4716961-stride-boring-sector-interesting-expected-returns\">Stride, Inc.</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LRN\" title=\"Stride, Inc.\">LRN</a></span>), in which I identified a significant opportunity ahead because of a deep valuation, amazing financials, and good opportunities to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1731919436/image_1731919436.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742344-stride-is-valuation-now-a-risk", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 18:20:02"}, {"id": "4742358", "title": "KNOT Offshore Partners LP Common Units 2024 Q3 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by KNOT Offshore Partners LP Common Units in conjunction with their 2024 Q3 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106043\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742358-knot-offshore-partners-lp-common-units-2024-q3-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 18:13:59"}, {"id": "4742339", "title": "BNY Mellon Equity Income Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1360003423/image_1360003423.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Hands exchanging cyber coins\" data-id=\"1360003423\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1370px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1360003423/image_1360003423.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1360003423/image_1360003423.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1360003423/image_1360003423.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1360003423/image_1360003423.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1360003423/image_1360003423.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1360003423/image_1360003423.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1360003423/image_1360003423.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1360003423/image_1360003423.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Describe the performance of the fund relative to its benchmark during the last three months.</strong></p> <p>Equity markets registered solid gains for the quarter as the long-awaited interest-rate cut by the US Federal Reserve (Fed) arrived. The Bank of England (BOE) and the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1360003423/image_1360003423.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742339-bny-mellon-equity-income-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 17:59:00"}, {"id": "4742336", "title": "Berkshire Hathaway Should Be Broken Up", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"BNSF Train, Burlington Northern Santa Fe\" data-id=\"506794609\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5580px\" height=\"3720px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">RiverNorthPhotography</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In our mind, <strong>Warren Buffett</strong> and <strong>Charlie Munger</strong> are two of the greatest investors of all time. One only needs to take a look at their track record for proof of this assertion.</p> <p>While their company, <strong>Berkshire Hathaway</strong> (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/506794609/image_506794609.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742336-berkshire-hathaway-should-be-broken-up", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 17:55:35"}, {"id": "4742335", "title": "Nuveen Churchill Direct Lending: Why I Am Following Insider And Buying This BDC", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1147449046/image_1147449046.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business development concept. Finding solution to growth.\" data-id=\"1147449046\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalph